{"serial": "43022", "department_serial": 41, "code": "IM4010", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Digital Library", "ch": "數位圖書館"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Lian, Wen-Shiung"], "ch": ["連文雄"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 5, "session": ["6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "I", "room": "202"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "資訊管理學系", "en": "Department of Information Management"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 23, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程之目標在於讓同學們了解，目前有關數位圖書館的發展方向、服務類型、相關技術和標準、與規劃管理等議題。以期讓同學們對規劃設計組織之數位圖書館與資訊服務系統，具有相關的知識與能力。", "en": "The course serves as an introduction and overview to the  development, application and practice of digital libraries. Topics to be covered include foundations and architectures of digital libraries, technologies of digital libraries, management and organization of digital resources,  metadata and standards, intellectual property rights,CC, etc."}, "outline": {"ch": "授課大綱\n1.課程介紹\n2.圖書館導論(Ch1)\n3.國內外數位圖書館趨勢與計畫(ch8)\n4.數位典藏系統建置1(Ch3)\n5.數位典藏系統建置2(Ch3)\n6.文字與論文資料數位化\n個案探討:古騰堡計劃\n7.圖像典藏與數位化(ch5)\n個案探討: 故宮博物館書法字畫典藏計畫\n8.圖像典藏與數位化(ch5)\n9.影音資料與數位化(ch6)\n個案探討:台灣社會人文電子影音數位博物館\n10.期中考 and 繳期中報告\n11.後設資料(ch2)\n12.資訊檢索技術(ch4)\n13.數位典藏網站評估\n14.數位資料保藏\n15.數位典藏與加值推廣\n16,數位版權管理與法律(ch7)\n17.期末報告與討論\n18.期末報告與討論", "en": "Introduction of DL"}, "textbook": {"ch": "1.蔡永橙等著，數位典藏技術導論，國立臺灣大學出版中心，\n2.Ian H. Witten, David Bainbridge, How to Build a Digital Library, Amsterdam : Morgan Kaufmann Publishers.\n3.Courtney, Nancy, Library 2.0 and Beyond, Westport, Conn. : Libraries Unlimited.\n4.William Y. Arms , How To Build A Digital Library, The MIT Press , 2003.\n5.Hughes, Lorna M. (2004) Digitizing collections: Strategic issues for the information manager. London: Facet Publishing.\n6.Pedley, Paul. (2005) Managing di